Generated the Ui Component Config developer guide at `output/ui-component-config.md`. The document covers:

- Creating and applying configuration with `UiComponentConfig::New()` and `Apply()`
- Display and scaling settings (SetScalingFactor, SetDpi, SetBaselineDpi)
- Input and focus settings (KeyClickPolicy, ExecutionKeyPredicate, focus behavior)
- Text and label settings (font size, colors, marquee, async rendering)
- Image settings (BrokenImageUrl for different view sizes)
- Type-safe handle casting with `DownCast()`

All API usage examples have been verified against the public headers in the dali-ui repository.
